Description: Indian Language Computing Library
 Silpa, Swathanthra Indian Language Processing Applications is a 
 web platform to host the free(dom) software language processing 
 applications easily. It is a web framework and a set of applications
 for processing Indian Languages in many ways. Or in other words,
 it is a platform for porting existing and upcoming language
 processing applications to the web. Silpa can also be used
 as a python library or as a webservice from other applications.
 
